{
  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Et Korus / Jezenexa Dehls / ta Dehla Kaâta/ ta Lewja Dehla / xehme pee few Datann un Abiramu / Eeliaba Dehls/ un Onnu/ Peleta Dehlu/ Riibena Dehls.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un zehlahs prett Mohsu/ lihds ar diwitints un peezdefimits Wihteen/ no teem Israêta Behrneem / tahs Draudses Wirsneekeln/ un pee tahs Draudses Aizinateem / un Wihteen no leelas Slawas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tee fapulzejahs prett Mohsu un prett Aâronu/un fazziia us teem: Juhs dands pahri darat / jo wiſch ta Drandse irr fwehta/ un tas KUNGS irr winno Widdii / kapehz pa-angastinajatees juhs pahr ta KUNGA Draudsibu?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Kad Mohsus to dsirdeja/ tad kritte wiſch us fawu Wai-gu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un wiſch runnaja us Koru/ un us wiſfu wiſza Pulku/un fazziia : Rihtâ agri/ tad dohs tas KUNGS Sinnu / kas winnam peederr / un kas fwehts irr / un kurru wiſch feruin liks uppureht/ un ko wiſch iswehlehs / lai tas winnam uppure.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Darrajt to / xemmeetees Rwehpja Trautus/ Korus/ un wiſs winna Pulks.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un xenmeet rihtâ Ugguni eeksch teem/ un leezeet Rwehpju-Sahles tur wiſu preeksh to KUNGU / un tas Wihrs/kurru tas KUNGS iswehlehs/ laid tas\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Mohsus fazziia us Koru : klausajt jelle juhs Lewja Behrni.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Irr tas juhs mas? ka ta Israêta Deewts juhs no tahs Israêta Draudses irr atschkihris ka wiſch juhs few peefchkirtu pee ta KUNGA Dsihtwofta Darbeem kalpoht / un preefsch tah Draudses stahweht / un teen pee Rohkas buht?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Wiſch irr teu/ un wiſ fus tawus Brahtus / tohs Lewja Behrnis ar teu pee few peeschkihris/ melkejat juhs nu arridsan to Preesteru-Ammatu?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tadeht tu/ un wiſs taw Pulks effet fagabjuschti prett te KUNGU / jo kas irr Aârons/ ka juhs pretti winnu effat kurneju-schi?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Mohsus nofuhtija Da-tann/ un Abiramu/ tohs Eeliaba Dehls aizinaht; bet tee fazziia mehs ne nahkam.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Irr tas wehl mas / ka fun muhs no weenas Semties/ kas ar Peenu un Meddu tekt/ effi is-weddis / nokaudains muhs Tuff-nefi? ka tu arridsan pats effi\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tu arr ne effi muhs wed-dis us weenu Semmi / kas ar Peenu un Meddu tekt / nedsmuns Tibrunus / un Wiyna-Dahrsus par Jhpaschimu de-wis/gribbi tu teem Wihteen tahs\n"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
  "notes": ""
}
